Notes: UWO's Mikolajczak sends game to overtime tied at 73 by making two free throws
with 2.5 seconds left in regulation...UWSP's Kraemer scores the game-winning
points on a layup with nine seconds left in overtime...UWO's Rosicky misses
bank shot at overtime horn...UWSP ties UWO for WIAC lead with one game left.
Game.Officials: Don Baumgart,  Brian Kenney & Wes Porter
